data.description: Nearly new home on the largest lot in Buffalo Highlands! This gem features an open layout, a chef's kitchen with stainless appliances and island, plus custom updates throughout. In your primary bedroom, you'll enjoy an en-suite bath with double sinks, and all bedrooms have walk-in closets. Convenient upstairs laundry room, washer and dryer included. Unfinished basement, just add drywall and your design touches. Completing this home are an attached two-car garage and an expansive backyard. A must-see!
